# Skill Ignore Patterns
# Use gitignore-style patterns to exclude files from skill loading

# Ignore draft skills
draft-*.md
**/draft-*.md
*-draft.md
**/*-draft.md

# Ignore test/example files
**/test-*.md
**/example-*.md

# Ignore template files
**/template.md
**/_template.md

# Ignore README files
README.md
**/README.md

# Ignore hidden files
**/.*

# Ignore backup files
**/*.bak
**/*.backup
**/*~
